00:03:08,298 --> 00:03:09,998
-Hei. -Hah?

30
00:03:09,998 --> 00:03:11,498
Apa yang sedang kau lakukan?

31
00:03:11,498 --> 00:03:13,298
Jasadnya ada di lantai dua.

32
00:03:13,298 --> 00:03:15,898
Kalian?

33
00:03:15,898 --> 00:03:17,898
Baik...

34
00:03:17,898 --> 00:03:19,698
Jadi kau mengatakan...

