102
00:06:20,098 --> 00:06:21,198
Ya.

103
00:06:21,198 --> 00:06:23,098
Itu yang Kyoko katakan.

104
00:06:23,098 --> 00:06:25,398
"Masahaschi Ninomiya (29)" -Tapi Harawaki memberitahuku

105
