106
00:06:28,898 --> 00:06:31,198
Apa dia membawanya dengannya?

107
00:06:31,198 --> 00:06:34,098
Ya, dia punya sebuah tablet mini.

108
00:06:34,098 --> 00:06:38,498
Dia selalu menyimpannya di saku jaketnya.

109
00:06:38,498 --> 00:06:39,498
