217
00:11:40,553 --> 00:11:42,753
Bicara soal masa-masa kuliahnya,

218
00:11:42,753 --> 00:11:44,553
kaos yang dia beli di toko itu

219
00:11:44,553 --> 00:11:47,353
Kyoko mengenakan kaos yang sama dalam video itu

220
00:11:47,353 --> 00:11:50,053
